SITEBANNER INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS

1. Install the necessary database tables:

$ mysql -p -u USER DBNAME < inc/app/sitebanner/install/install-mysql.sql
(enter password when prompted)

2. Copy the banner collection definition into the cms app:

$ cd /PATH/TO/SITELLITE
$ cp -R inc/app/sitebanner/install/sitebanner_ad.php inc/app/cms/conf/collections/

3. Call sitebanner/display in your templates and/or sidebars, and create some
banners.

That's all there is to it!
